_sText:
It seriously doesn't mean a map ain't good if it didn't take 10 days to make.
This, ( Don't take this as anything like cocky etc. ) is one of the examples. It took me ~4 hours to make, and it ain't a bad map. It has a unique design and nice lighting and not too complex playability.

I also added the HDR effect for your you, so if your computer can handle it enable bloom!

I will be maybe soon submitting another map for this particular gamemode, but the problem is I can't get it compiled because it is on my other computer and the computer crashes when I try to compile.

Have fun playing this map, and don't take the game too seriously!
